/-- A set `A` is balanced if `a ‚Ä¢ A` is contained in `A` whenever `a`
has norm less than or equal to one. -/
def balanced (A : set E) := ‚àÄ a : ùïú, ‚à•a‚à• ‚â§ 1 ‚Üí a ‚Ä¢ A ‚äÜ A

